Small Business Development - Core Tools

SBDevCore is framework for building sites focused on non web based businesses that enables developers to quickly push out a professional feature rich site that clients/business owners can self-manage.
Framework is designed to be easily extendAble to add custom resources, singular pages, and features

To get started create a new rails app, add the sbdevcore gem and run the sbdevcore:install (app name) generator script followed by sbdevcore:seed rake script.

From there you should be able to start a rails server and have a fully functional site with some basic pages.

To add text, photos, downloadable files, galleries, and embed youtube videos sign in with admin/secret and use the in page buttons.